title: SPY's Happy Hour—March 21st, 2014—with mmx and Chad Larson
description: Chad Larson, a Doctor of Naturopathic Medicine and Chiropractor, visits SPY's Happy Hour to discuss the healing properties of nature to which humans are subjected on a regular basis. Dr. Larson explains that as we reconnect to and appreciate the products of nature, we reinvigorate our vital force (vis) and become part of an ensuing environment in which we enjoy health and happiness.
